T1	Participants 827 1123	Prospective study over 16 weeks of children randomized to receive prednisolone (40 mg/m2) or dexamethasone (6.5 mg/m2) as part of the MRC-ALL97/99 induction chemotherapy for ALL. Nineteen children (8 male, 11 female) with a median age 5.9 years (range 2.6-13 years) were recruited into the study.
